  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Site Supervisor(Construction)",
  "description": "<p>We are seeking 3 Construction Supervisors to oversee daily construction site operations and ensure works are carried out safely, efficiently and according to project requirements.<br />Key Responsibilities:</p><p>•\tSupervise and manage daily site activities and construction workers</p><p>•\tCoordinate and assign tasks to workers and subcontractors</p><p>•\tEnsure construction works are carried out according to drawings and schedule</p><p>•\tMonitor site progress, quality of workmanship and safety compliance</p><p>•\tLiaise with project managers, subcontractors and suppliers</p><p>•\tResolve site issues and ensure smooth site operations</p><p>•\tPrepare basic site reports and daily work updates</p><p></p><p>⸻</p><p></p><p>Job Requirements</p><p>•\tMinimum 2–3 years of relevant construction site experience</p><p>•\tExperience in supervising construction workers and site activities</p><p>•\tFamiliar with construction safety requirements and site practices</p><p>•\tAble to work independently and manage site operations</p><p>•\tGood communication and coordination skills</p><p></p><p>(Singapore Citizens and Permanent Residents are welcome to apply)</p><p></p><p>⸻</p><p></p><p>Work Location</p><p></p><p>Singapore (project sites / company-assigned locations)</p><p></p><p>⸻</p><p></p><p>Working Hours</p><p></p><p>6-day work week</p><p>Working hours as per site requirements</p><p></p>",
